data.description: Newer home, only 2 years old. Split bedroom floor plan. Open floor plan, great for entertaining. All vinyl plank waterproof flooring throughout the house with tile in the bathrooms. Granite countertops in the kitchen and bathrooms. All stainless steel appliances in the kitchen. Center island with Granite countertop and lots of storage can seat 2-4. Eat-in space in the kitchen. Large back yard to grow your family in. House is on septic and well water. The Well is a deep water well so no filtration system is needed. Inside laundry room off of the kitchen. The master bathroom has double vanities and walk-in shower. Guest bathroom has a tub/shower combo. Call for your appointment today!!!
